description: Defines a Schedule class representing a timetable entry for a kindergarten management system, including properties for class details, timing, and methods for mapping and copying.

classes.name: Schedule
classes.description: Represents a scheduled class with properties like className, subject, start/end times, day of week, teacher ID, room, description, and active status. Includes methods for serialization, copying, and generating a time range string.

methods.name: toMap
methods.description: Serializes the Schedule instance into a map suitable for storage or transmission.

methods.name: fromMap
methods.description: Creates a Schedule instance from a map, typically retrieved from storage.

methods.name: copyWith
methods.description: Creates a copy of the Schedule object with optional overridden properties.

methods.name: timeRange
methods.description: Returns a string representing the start and end times in HH:MM - HH:MM format.
